  <entry>
    <title>Markdown食用方法（未完待续）</title>
    <link href="https://kunzhiyi.github.io/posts/2.html"/>
    <id>https://kunzhiyi.github.io/posts/2.html</id>
    <published>2022-07-24T11:21:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-24T15:39:59.498Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="为什么选择markdown语言"><a href="#为什么选择markdown语言" class="headerlink" title="为什么选择markdown语言"></a>为什么选择markdown语言</h1><p>Markdown 是一种轻量级标记语言，支持多种格式，同时也是编写本博客所需的语言！</p><h1 id="快捷键"><a href="#快捷键" class="headerlink" title="快捷键"></a>快捷键</h1><table><thead><tr><th>功能</th><th>快捷键</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>加粗</td><td>Ctrl + B</td></tr><tr><td>斜体</td><td>Ctrl + I</td></tr><tr><td>引用</td><td>Ctrl + Q</td></tr><tr><td>插入链接</td><td>Ctrl + L</td></tr><tr><td>插入代码</td><td>Ctrl + K</td></tr><tr><td>插入图片</td><td>Ctrl + G</td></tr><tr><td>提升标题</td><td>Ctrl + H</td></tr><tr><td>有序列表</td><td>Ctrl + O</td></tr><tr><td>无序列表</td><td>Ctrl + U</td></tr><tr><td>横线</td><td>Ctrl + R</td></tr><tr><td>撤销</td><td>Ctrl + Z</td></tr><tr><td>重做</td><td>Ctrl + Y</td></tr></tbody></table><h1 id="基础语法"><a href="#基础语法" class="headerlink" title="基础语法"></a>基础语法</h1><h2 id="分级标题"><a href="#分级标题" class="headerlink" title="分级标题"></a>分级标题</h2><ul><li><p>一级标题对应一个<code>#</code>号加空格；</p></li><li><p>二级标题对应两个<code>#</code>号加空格；</p></li><li><p>以此类推，共支持六级标题；</p></li></ul><p>如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-markdown" data-language="markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">#</span> 一级标题</span><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">##</span> 二级标题</span><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">###</span> 三级标题</span><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">####</span> 四级标题</span><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">#####</span> 五级标题</span><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">######</span> 六级标题</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="字体设置"><a href="#字体设置" class="headerlink" title="字体设置"></a>字体设置</h2><ul><li><em>斜体文本</em>：在文本两边添加一个星号<code>*</code>或下划线<code>_</code>；</li><li><strong>粗体文本</strong>：在文本两边添加两个星号<code>**</code>或下划线<code>_</code>；</li><li><strong><em>斜粗体文本</em></strong>：在文本两边添加三个星号<code>***</code>或下划线<code>_</code>；</li><li><u>下划线</u>：在文本两边分别添加<code>&lt;u&gt;</code>和<code>&lt;\u&gt;</code>；</li><li><del>删除线</del>：在文本两边添加两个个波浪线<code>~~</code>；</li></ul><p>本文使用<code>*</code>，如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-markdown" data-language="markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token italic"><span class="token punctuation">*</span><span class="token content">斜体文本</span><span class="token punctuation">*</span></span><span class="token bold"><span class="token punctuation">**</span><span class="token content">粗体文本</span><span class="token punctuation">**</span></span><span class="token bold"><span class="token punctuation">**</span><span class="token content"><span class="token italic"><span class="token punctuation">*</span><span class="token content">斜粗体文本</span><span class="token punctuation">*</span></span></span><span class="token punctuation">**</span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>u</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>下划线<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>\u</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span><span class="token strike"><span class="token punctuation">~~</span><span class="token content">删除线</span><span class="token punctuation">~~</span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h2><ul><li>无序列表，使用星号(<code>*</code>)、加号(<code>+</code>)或是减号(<code>-</code>)，再加一个空格作为列表标记；</li><li>有序列表，使用数字并加上 <code>.</code> 号，再加一个空格作为列表标记；</li></ul><p>如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-markdown" data-language="markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token list punctuation">*</span> 无序列表 1<span class="token list punctuation">+</span> 无序列表 2<span class="token list punctuation">-</span> 无序列表 3<span class="token list punctuation">1.</span> 有序列表 1<span class="token list punctuation">2.</span> 有序列表 2<span class="token list punctuation">3.</span> 有序列表 3<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>如果要控制列表的层级，则需要在列表符号后使用 <code>tab</code></li></ul><p>如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-markdown" data-language="markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token list punctuation">+</span> 无序列表 <span class="token list punctuation">+</span> 无序列表 <span class="token list punctuation">1.</span> 有序列表<span class="token list punctuation">1.</span>有序列表<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>例：</p><ul><li><p>无序列表 </p><ul><li>无序列表 </li></ul></li></ul><ol><li>有序列表<ol><li>有序列表</li></ol></li></ol><h2 id="网页链接"><a href="#网页链接" class="headerlink" title="网页链接"></a>网页链接</h2><ul><li><ul><li><code>[链接名称](链接地址)</code></li><li><code>链接地址</code></li></ul></li></ul><p>如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-markdown" data-language="markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token url">[<span class="token content">链接名称</span>](连接地址)</span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>链接地址</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span> 或 直接复制链接地址<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="插入图片"><a href="#插入图片" class="headerlink" title="插入图片"></a>插入图片</h2><hr><p>未完待续</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;为什么选择markdown语言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#为什么选择markdown语言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;为什么选择markdown语言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;为什么选择markdown语言&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Markdown 是一种轻量级标记语</summary>
      
    
    
    
